# 🎓 EduPlay – A Fun & Interactive Learning App for Kids  

This repository contains the **UI/UX Case Study** for **EduPlay**, an interactive mobile application designed to make learning fun and engaging for children.  

---

## 📖 Project Overview  
EduPlay is a mobile app aimed at children, combining education with play.  
The app focuses on:  
- Gamified learning experiences  
- Interactive lessons & quizzes  
- Colorful, kid-friendly design  
- Parental dashboard for progress tracking  

